\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma:\Lp 2{\psi}\longrightarrow\R
\]

\end_inset

by
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma\left(f\right):=\lebInt{\nu}f
\]

\end_inset

and notice that 
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
